</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-37_ pf-text-1"><strong>Civil partner</strong> - A person who has entered into a civil partnership with another person of the same sex.</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-39_ pf-text-1"><strong>Dissolution </strong>- The legal ending of a civil partnership, akin to divorce in a marriage.
